        <div class="msgSubject">Lancer 101 updated- 10/4/10</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-02 04:40:23 | Edited: Oct 04 2010  5:55am  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1286016023267724812" id="quote-1286016023267724812" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1286016023267724812" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=186&amp;mid=1286016023267724812&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1286016023267724812&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1286016023267724812" onclick="followToggle('add','1286016023267724812')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
